text: Chand Mohammad is an Indian politician. He was elected as MLA of Bhagabangola Vidhan Sabha Constituency in 2006 and 2011. He is an All India Trinamool Congress politician. ==References== Category:Living people Category:All India Trinamool Congress politicians Category:West Bengal MLAs 2006–2011 Category:West Bengal MLAs 2011–2016 Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
